OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSergeant shot dead by      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fsoldier with 'poor         
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Feyesight'                  
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, An army sergeant was shot and killed   
OL,6, when he was mistaken for a target by a 
OL,7, soldier with "poor eyesight", an       
OL,8, inquiry has found.                     
OL,10,FSgt Gavin Hillier died during a live   
OL,11,Ffire exercise at Castlemartin base in  
OL,12,FPembrokeshire on 4 March 2021.         
OL,14,FThe inquiry found a contributory factor
OL,15,Fwas that the soldier, referred to as   
OL,16,FGuardsman 1, was not wearing           
OL,17,Fprescription lenses at the time.       
OL,19,FBut the report went on to say that he  
OL,20,Fdid not have service-issued spectacles.
